sources.title: Flying Blind (1941) Richard Arlen & Jean Parker | Full Length Comedy, Spy Movie
sources.description:
A plane-load of thrills ... as two lovers battle spies in the skies! A spy steals a secret military device, then hijacks an airliner to get away. The airliner crashes in the wilderness & the survivors are threatened by a raging forest fire.
 
Director: Frank McDonald
Writers: Maxwell Shane, Richard Murphy
Stars: Richard Arlen, Jean Parker, Nils Asther 
Genres: Classics, Comedy, Drama
